PF2
k_2=\dfrac{t}{a-c}=tan\angle PF2T2
\angle T2PF2=\dfrac{\pi}{2}-\angle PF2T2
tan \angle T2PF2=\dfrac{1}{tan\angle PF2T2}=\dfrac{a-c}{t}=tan(A_2-A_1)
